title: #92Noon! 11a Hour 8/10 - Gabe Henderson, Ryan Grigson
description: VEN's Gabe Henderson stops by TCO to talk all things football and Vikings Training Camp. Plus, Vikings Senior Vice President of Player Personnel Ryan Grigson to talk making Minnesota his home, the player he's most proud of scouting, & more!
